{
  "texts": [
    "We report the accuracy in %.",
    "Erdős baseline (w/ zero temperature) is shaded.",
    "For the edge encoding, edge = edge list, adjl = adjacency list, adjm = adjacency matrix.",
    "For sorting, s = source and t = target, and the entry represents the sorting key.",
    "Shuffling is applied to all remaining ambiguities; in this case we report the mean accuracy ± std over 10 seeds.Qwen-3B G1-3B Comp."
  ]
}